title: Episode 39: A Trader Joe's Shopping List of Fabulous Fall Finds
itunes:title: A Trader Joe's Shopping List of Fabulous Fall Finds
description:
Once again, we’re falling head over pumpkin for fall. In this episode of Inside Trader Joe’s you’ll get a sneak peek at some of our favorite new stuff, like Pumpkin Alfredo Sauce and Pumpkin Oat Beverage, and even some things that have no pumpkin at all (gasp!), like Butternut Mac & Cheese Bites and Maple Walnut Biscotti. Grab a pen and a piece of paper - you’re going to want to make a list.
